# üß† CodeGlia ‚Äì AI-Powered Multi-Language Vulnerability Scanner

CodeGlia is an AI-augmented vulnerability detection platform integrating **Bandit**, **Semgrep**, and **Google Gemini API** for multi-language code analysis.  
It generates interactive HTML dashboards, CVE mappings, and a "Trust Score" metric to quantify code security.

